### ELL14 Rotator (RS-485 Bus)

```rust
use daq_hardware::drivers::ell14::Ell14Bus;

let bus = Ell14Bus::open("/dev/ttyUSB0").await?;
let rotator = bus.device("2").await?;  // Gets calibrated device
rotator.move_abs(45.0).await?;
```

